.\" bunny.1 - man page for the Bunny CLI
.TH BUNNY 1 "2026-04-08" "bunny" "Bunny CLI Manual"
.SH NAME
bunny \- manage bunny.net resources from the command line
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bunny
.RI [ command ]
.RI [ subcommand ]
.RI [ flags ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bunny
is a command-line interface for the bunny.net CDN platform. It provides
access to pull zones, storage zones, DNS zones, video streaming, edge
scripting, and Shield security features through the bunny.net API.
.PP
Before using most commands, configure authentication with
.BR "bunny configure" .
.SH GLOBAL FLAGS
These flags apply to all commands:
.TP
.BI \-\-api\-key " string"
bunny.net API key. Overrides config file and
.B BUNNY_API_KEY
environment variable.
.TP
.BI \-\-output " string"
Output format:
.BR table " (default),"
.BR json ", or"
.BR json\-pretty .
.TP
.BI \-f ", " \-\-field " string"
Comma-separated list of fields to display in output.
.TP
.BI \-\-jq " string"
Filter JSON output with a jq expression (built-in, no external
.BR jq (1)
required).
.SH COMMANDS
.SS Configuration
.TP
.B bunny configure
Interactive setup wizard. Prompts for API key.
Saves to
.IR ~/.config/bunny/config.toml .
.SS Pull Zones
.TP
.B bunny pullzones list
List pull zones. Supports
.BR \-\-search ,
.BR \-\-limit ,
and
.BR \-\-all .
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones get " id
Show pull zone details. Supports
.BR \-\-watch .
.TP
.B bunny pullzones create
Create a pull zone with
.BR \-\-name ,
.BR \-\-origin\-url ,
.BR \-\-type ,
or
.BR \-\-from\-file .
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones update " id
Update a pull zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones delete " id
Delete a pull zone. Requires
.BR \-\-yes .
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones hostnames list " pull_zone_id
List hostnames for a pull zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones hostnames add " pull_zone_id
Add a hostname with
.BR \-\-hostname .
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones hostnames remove " pull_zone_id
Remove a hostname.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones purge " pull_zone_id
Purge the cache. Optionally filter by
.BR \-\-tag .
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones edge\-rules list " pull_zone_id
List edge rules.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones edge\-rules add " pull_zone_id
Add or update an edge rule.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones edge\-rules delete " "pull_zone_id edge_rule_id"
Delete an edge rule.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones edge\-rules enable " "pull_zone_id edge_rule_id"
Enable an edge rule.
.TP
.BI "bunny pullzones edge\-rules disable " "pull_zone_id edge_rule_id"
Disable an edge rule.
.SS Storage Zones
.TP
.B bunny storagezones list
List storage zones. Supports
.BR \-\-search ,
.BR \-\-limit ,
.BR \-\-all ,
and
.BR \-\-include\-deleted .
.TP
.BI "bunny storagezones get " id
Show storage zone details.
.TP
.B bunny storagezones create
Create a storage zone with
.BR \-\-name ,
.BR \-\-region ,
.BR \-\-replication\-regions ,
.BR \-\-zone\-tier .
.TP
.BI "bunny storagezones update " id
Update a storage zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny storagezones delete " id
Delete a storage zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny storagezones reset\-password " id
Reset the storage zone password.
.SS Edge Storage
.TP
.BI "bunny storage ls " zone/path
List files in a storage zone directory.
.TP
.BI "bunny storage cp " "src dst"
Copy files to or from Edge Storage. If
.I src
is a local file, uploads it; otherwise downloads.
.TP
.BI "bunny storage rm " zone/path
Delete a file from Edge Storage.
.PP
Edge Storage commands use per-zone passwords. Override with
.B \-\-hostname
and
.BR \-\-password .
.SS DNS Zones
.TP
.B bunny dns list
List DNS zones. Supports
.BR \-\-search ,
.BR \-\-limit ,
and
.BR \-\-all .
.TP
.BI "bunny dns get " id
