.TP
.BI "bunny dns import " zone_id
Import DNS records from a zone file with
.BR \-\-file .
.TP
.BI "bunny dns export " zone_id
Export DNS zone to zone file format.
.TP
.BI "bunny dns records list " zone_id
List DNS records in a zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny dns records add " zone_id
Add a DNS record with
.BR \-\-type ,
.BR \-\-name ,
.BR \-\-value .
.TP
.BI "bunny dns records update " "zone_id record_id"
Update a DNS record.
.TP
.BI "bunny dns records delete " "zone_id record_id"
Delete a DNS record.
.TP
.BI "bunny dns dnssec enable " zone_id
Enable DNSSEC for a zone.
.TP
.BI "bunny dns dnssec disable " zone_id
Disable DNSSEC for a zone.
